get the year as input 
fetch max population and min population

value = input(' please Enter Year: ')
x = max(Populationdata[value])
y = min(Populationdata[value])

initialized these variables with 0
template= 0
sum=0

for loop then if else statement
to access the country name subsequent to that index.
 if(column != x):
  template = template+1
 else:
  break

for column in Populationdata[value]:
 if(column != y):
   sum = sum+1
 else:
  break

pass the index and get the country name 
first_column = Populationdata.iloc[:, 0]



print("Lowest Population is:",first_column[sum])
print("Highest Population is:",first_column[template])
